  centered within the 66dp "safe zone" of the 108dp adaptive-icon canvas
  (system may crop/mask up to 18dp on each edge depending on launcher
  shape). Replaces the unmodified Android Studio template default
  (generic Android robot-adjacent glyph). Also reused as the monochrome
  variant (see mipmap-anydpi-v26/ic_launcher.xml) since it's already a
  flat single-color mark.
-->
